SpoonerPlacements.Note: Even on a good day, Los Santos can be a disorientating place. On a bad day, you're upside down in a closed loop, you can only see the next three feet of track, and you can't remember if you're driving one of the world's fastest cars or a fixed-wing stunt plane. Gotta love the bad days. Lap Transform Race starting in Super cars, also featuring the Mallard.
